  "reference_number": "MYA0065",
  "remarks": "\nWin Kyaw Kyaw Aung is an involved person under The Myanmar (Sanctions) Regulations 2021 because, as a former director and shareholder of Asia Sun Trading Company Limited, he has been involved in the repression of the civilian population in Myanmar by making available economic resources (aviation fuel) directly or indirectly to or for the benefit of the Myanmar security forces. \n",
